      "Blanket Liability Waiver for Landlord Negligence: A lease term releasing the landlord from liability for injuries or damages caused by the landlord's own negligence is generally unenforceable as contrary to Missouri public policy.",
      "Occupancy Cap Below Two Per Bedroom: A lease that sets a cap lower than two persons per bedroom is presumptively unreasonable under RSMo 441.043 and may also conflict with federal Fair Housing Act familial-status protections."
